"title": "5555: stealing",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5555: stealing",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Theft is always condemned in Scripture, though the possibility of mitigating circumstances is recognised. Converted thieves must show their repentance, if possible, in a practical way.</p>\n<h2>Stealing is condemned as a sin</h2>\n<h3>It is prohibited</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:15\">EXO 20:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:19\">DEU 5:19</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:11\">LEV 19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:10\">PSA 62:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:19\">MRK 10:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:20\">LUK 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:21\">ROM 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:9\">ROM 13:9</a></p>\n<h3>Punishment for stealing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:10\">1CO 6:9–6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:16\">EXO 21:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:1-Exod22:4\">EXO 22:1–22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:2-Lev6:5\">LEV 6:2–6:5</a></p>\n<h3>The disgrace of thieves</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:26\">JER 2:26</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The company of thieves is to be avoided</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:24\">PRO 29:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:23\">ISA 1:23</a></p>\n<h3>Stealing is denied</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen44:8\">GEN 44:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:3-1Sam12:5\">1SA 12:3–12:5</a></p>\n<h2>Mitigating circumstances for stealing</h2>\n<h3>Poverty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:30-Prov6:31\">PRO 6:30–6:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:7-Prov30:9\">PRO 30:7–30:9</a></p>\n<h2>Stealing is commonplace in this world</h2>\n<h3>It is part of life in a sinful world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:2\">HOS 4:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19\">MAT 15:19</a></p>\n<h3>Roadside robbery</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:30\">LUK 10:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:10-Prov1:15\">PRO 1:10–1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:26\">2CO 11:26</a></p>\n<h3>Sheep stealing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:2\">JOB 24:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:4\">2SA 12:4</a></p>\n<h3>Dishonesty in trade</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:17\">JER 22:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:18\">EZK 28:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:7\">HOS 12:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:5\">AMO 8:5</a></p>\n<h3>Dishonest tax collectors</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:13\">LUK 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:8\">LUK 19:8</a></p>\n<h3>Theft in the temple</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:12-Matt21:13\">MAT 21:12–21:13</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:15-Mark11:17\">MRK 11:15–11:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:45-Luke19:46\">LUK 19:45–19:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:11\">JER 7:11</a></p>\n<h3>Theft in the family</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:19\">GEN 31:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:1-Judg17:2\">JDG 17:1–17:2</a></p>\n<h3>Wife stealing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:3\">2SA 11:3</a></p>\n<h3>Kidnapping</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:2\">2KI 11:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr22:11\">2CH 22:11</a></p>\n<h3>Temple robbers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:37\">ACT 19:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:22\">ROM 2:22</a></p>\n<h3>Body stealing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:64\">MAT 27:64</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of stealing</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:19\">GEN 31:19</a> <em>Rachel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:11\">JOS 7:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:20-Josh7:21\">JOS 7:20–7:21</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:1-Judg17:2\">JDG 17:1–17:2</a> <em>Micah the Ephraimite</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:38\">MAT 27:38</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:27\">MRK 15:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:44\">MAT 27:44</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:32\">LUK 23:32</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:6\">JHN 12:6</a> <em>Judas</em></p>\n<h2>Stealing as an image</h2>\n<h3>Of forbidden pleasures</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:17\">PRO 9:17</a></p>\n<h3>Of a captivated heart</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:6\">2SA 15:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:9\">SNG 4:9</a></p>\n<h3>Of unexpected loss</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:10-Prov6:11\">PRO 6:10–6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:33-Prov24:34\">PRO 24:33–24:34</a></p>\n<h3>Of God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:2\">1TH 5:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:9-Jer49:10\">JER 49:9–49:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:5-Obad1:6\">OBA 1:5–1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:42-Matt24:44\">MAT 24:42–24:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:10\">2PE 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual stealing</h2>\n<h3>Stealing from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:8-Mal3:9\">MAL 3:8–3:9</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Lying prophets</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:30\">JER 23:30</a></p>\n<h3>False shepherds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:1\">JHN 10:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:8\">JHN 10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:10\">JHN 10:10</a></p>\n<h2>Converted thieves</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:39-Luke23:43\">LUK 23:39–23:43</a> <em>the thief on the cross</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:9–6:11</a> <em>some of the Corinthians</em></p>\n<h3>Repentance must be borne out in practical actions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:28\">EPH 4:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:15\">EZK 33:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:8\">LUK 19:8</a> <em>Zacchaeus</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:10\">TIT 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>There is no stealing in heaven</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:20\">MAT 6:20</a></strong></p>",
